<section class="project-content">
  <div class="summary">
    <h2>Built a resource for the design community</h2>
    <p class="summary-text">designed and shipped a design resource to find both free and paid font inspiration for your next project</p>
  </div>
  <div class="project-role">
    <h3>Context</h3>
    <p><a target=”_blank” href="http://www.fontsinthewild.com/">live website</a>, with real users. currently designing + coding features such as filtering and sorting fonts for specific use cases and categories</p>
    <h3 class="role">Role</h3>
    <p>sole UI designer and fullstack developer. During quarantine I wanted to build a resource to give back to the design community and saw the gap in the market
    + challenge to find quality, open source fonts</p>
