<section class="problem">
  <h2>the problem ✍️</h2>
  <p>the core problem i am trying to solve with <a target=”_blank” style="text-decoration: underline;" href="http://www.fontsinthewild.com/">fonts in the wild </a>is the challenge of finding quality, free fonts. i spoke with many designers and developers who struggle to find free type inspiration. current resources, such as Typewolf focus on expensive fonts with no option to filter through accessible options.</p>
</section>
